<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c2">(٢٣)</span> ... <span class="c3">{كَاسًا}</span> ... مِنَ الخَمْرِ.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c2">(٢٣)</span> ... <span class="c3">{لَّا لَغْوٌ فِيهَا}</span> ... لَا كَلَامٌ سَاقِطٌ أَثْنَاءَ شُرْبِهَا.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c2">(٢٣)</span> ... <span class="c3">{وَلَا تَاثِيمٌ}</span> ... وَلَا يَقَعُ بِسَبَبِهَا إِثْمٌ فِي قَوْلٍ أَوْ فِعْلٍ.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c2">(٢٤)</span> ... <span class="c3">{مَّكْنُونٌ}</span> ... مَصُونٌ، مَسْتُورٌ فِي أَصْدَافِهِ.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span><span class="c2">(٢٦)</span> ... <span class="c3">{مُشْفِقِينَ}</span> ... خَائِفِينَ مِنَ العَذَابِ.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span><span class="c2">(٢٧)</span> ... <span class="c3">{عَذَابَ السَّمُومِ}</span> ... عَذَابَ النَّارِ الَّتِي تَنْفُذُ فِي المَسَامِّ.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span><span class="c2">(٢٨)</span> ... <span class="c3">{الْبَرُّ}</span> ... المُحْسِنُ، كَثِيرُ الخَيْرِ.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span><span class="c2">(٢٩)</span> ... <span class="c3">{بِنِعْمَتِ رَبِّكَ}</span> ... بِسَبَبِ إِنْعَامِ اللهِ عَلَيْكَ بِالنُّبُوَّةِ، وَرَجَاحَةِ العَقْلِ.<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
